    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card title 'Reconstruct: OpenMS' does not align with the paper's actual research focus. The paper presents FeatureFinderMetabo, a novel algorithm for automated label-free quantification of metabolites from LC-MS data, not a reconstruction or documentation project.",
        "The research_question field contains only a license badge and bug-reporting instructions, not an actual research question. This appears to be extracted from documentation or a README file rather than the paper itself.",
        "The expected_outputs list contains specific figure filenames (PNG/SVG files) and a bug-reporting template that are not part of the paper's scientific outputs. These appear to be from OpenMS software documentation or a GitHub repository, not from this research paper.",
        "The card conflates the OpenMS software framework (which the algorithm is implemented in) with the research paper itself. The paper is a scientific study of a feature-detection algorithm; it is not a software reconstruction or documentation project."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 4,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_001",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
