      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper is about metabolomics (label-free quantification of metabolites from LC-MS data), not proteomics. No mention of peptide identification, MS/MS spectra, database search scoring, or peptide-spectrum matching. The paper focuses on feature detection and metabolite quantification, not evidence linking for peptide identifications.",
