      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Evidence linking is the process of connecting identified peptides and proteins from mass spectrometry data to supporting spectral evidence, database matches, and quantification metrics. In OpenMS workflows, this involves tracing peptide identifications back to their parent MS/MS ",
