      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The algorithm is available as part of the open-source software package OpenMS and runs on all major operating systems... The feature-detection algorithm presented in this work was implemented and integrated in the open-source framework OpenMS (version 1.10) as the software tool FeatureFinderMetabo.",
      "asbval:note": "OpenMS is confirmed as the implementation platform for FeatureFinderMetabo (check 1 passes). However, the paper does not discuss OpenMS maintainers performing severity assignment or release impact classification. The paper describes OpenMS as the target for implementation, not as a review/severity-assignment system. The role claimed in the card is not supported by the paper.",
