      "asbval:note": "Python is mentioned once in the paper in the context of data analysis ('All further analyses were conducted with the MATLAB R2012b (33) and R 2.15.2 (34) software packages'), but Python is not used for the primary analysis. The related_skills list describes meta-skills about expert review preparation, evidence linking, and reproducibility assessment\u2014none of which are the subject of this paper. This appears to be a generic skill card entry unrelated to the paper's content.",
