      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms OpenMS and TOPP framework, but does NOT mention '150+ TOPP Tools' or 'CTD parameter schema' by name. The paper discusses XML-based configuration files (*.ini) but does not use the term 'CTD' (Common Tool Definition). The claim about tool count and CTD is not verbatim in the passages.",
