      "asbval:evidence_quote": "OpenMS offers the functionality to build custom processing and analysis pipelines through the graphical workflow editor TOPPAS (22). We employed TOPPAS to construct an example workflow for label-free metabolite quantification... In order to allow for easy integration of downstream analysis methods such as statistical learning, we implemented this workflow in KNIME, a powerful platform for information mining (39).",
